			<![CDATA[1.  The new keyboard is much more comfortable than the old one.
     The old keyboard is not <blank word="nearly as comfortable as" blanksize="Large"/> (<i>nearly</i>) the new one.

2.  The M2 microphone is good, but the L2 microphone is a little better.
     The M2 microphone is <blank word="almost as good as"/>(<i>almost</i>) the L2 microphone.

3.  The Kol CD drive and the Dex CD drive are both very fast.
     The Kol CD drive is <blank word="just as fast as"/> (<i>just</i>) the Dex CD drive.

4.  The old printer is much noisier than the new one.
     The new printer is not <blank word="nearly as noisy as"/>(<i>nearly</i>) the old one.

5.  Star’s web cam is popular, but Brown’s web cam is a little more popular.
     Star’s web cam is <blank word="almost as popular as"/>(<i>almost</i>) Brown’s web cam. 

6.  The TA scanner costs US$250. The WB scanner costs US$230.
     The WB scanner does not cost <blank word="quite as much as"/> (<i>quite</i>) the TA scanner.]]>
